@startuml kv_client_triage_init_step
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam defaultFontName "SansSerif"
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title KV Client 定位定界（步骤1: Init）\nInit 建连：RPC + UDS 传 fd + URMA/UB + mmap；可与「可见 StatusCode 说明」对照

actor "测试/开发/Agent" as T
participant "client1\nSDK" as C
participant "worker1\n入口Worker" as W1
participant "OS/syscall" as OS
participant "URMA" as U

T -> C : 发起 Init
activate C

C -> C : 参数校验(host/port/凭证)
alt 参数非法
  note right of C
    责任团队: 接口调用方/业务方
    现象: K_INVALID
    建议: 先修参数再复测
  end note
  C --> T : Init失败(K_INVALID)
  deactivate C
  return
end

C -> W1 : RegisterClient (RPC)
activate W1
alt 连接失败/超时
  note right of W1
    责任团队: RPC/网络中间件团队
    现象: 1002/1001, Register client failed
    建议: 查监听端口/路由/防火墙
  end note
  W1 --> C : Status=1002/1001
  deactivate W1
  C --> T : Init失败(RPC)
  deactivate C
  return
end

C -> OS : recvmsg/sendmsg (UDS传fd)
alt fd异常/EOF/invalid fd
  note right of OS
    责任团队: OS/运行环境团队
    现象: invalid fd / Unexpected EOF
    建议: 查fd上限、UDS时序、对端进程状态
  end note
end

C -> U : urma_init + create_* + import/advise_jfr
alt URMA初始化或握手失败
  note right of U
    责任团队: RDMA/URMA团队
    现象: 1004 / Failed to urma...
    建议: 查UMDK/设备名/bonding/驱动
  end note
  C -> C : 记录错误，可回退TCP
else URMA成功
  C -> C : 进入UB可用状态
end

C -> OS : mmap (UB pool)
alt 内存映射失败
  note right of OS
    责任团队: OS/容量团队
    现象: K_OUT_OF_MEMORY(6)
    建议: 查内存限制与vm.max_map_count
  end note
end

W1 --> C : Init完成
deactivate W1
C --> T : Init成功(可能UB降级)
deactivate C

@enduml
